  "description": "Proxy-mode traffic surface: HTTP requests, SSE streams, tool calls, admission decisions, LLM bridge, Cisco Inspect, and the LLM judge + verdict cache. These panels only show data when DefenseClaw runs in proxy/router mode (openclaw, zeptoclaw). NOTE: this board is intentionally GLOBAL and deliberately has no $connector template variable \u2014 the HTTP / tool / judge / admission metrics here are emitted per proxy process and are not tagged with a hook connector / source / tool=<connector>:<event> dimension. For per-connector breakdowns use the Hook Connectors and Connector Detail dashboards.",
